data.description: Embark on a journey of grandeur with this awe-inspiring 2-story residence, spanning over 3,260 sqft and featuring 5 generously-sized bedrooms and 3.5 lavishly appointed bathrooms. Positioned majestically on one of the most sought-after lots in the community, it offers mesmerizing views of a tranquil, expansive lake. Step inside, and the open layout beckons you into a capacious living room seamlessly merging with a kitchen that defines spacious dining-living areas. Downstairs, two bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms provide convenience, while upstairs reveals 2 additional bedrooms, a master suite, and a sprawling den with a separate office/gaming room. Every bedroom boasts ample space and features jack and jill bathrooms, with the master suite showcasing an expansive walk-in closet and a screened patio. Adding to the allure, a brand-new roof installed in December 2023 ensures both style and substance. Conveniently located with easy access to the airport, major highways, upscale restaurants, shopping plazas, and retail stores, this home is poised and ready for its new owner. Seize the opportunity to make this haven yours – act now and indulge in the epitome of luxury living! LOW HOA fees!
